Installing ansible

check if pip installed 
$which pip

install ansible 
sudo pip install ansible

upgrade pip
sudo pip install --upgrade pip

specify what agent to use when running ad-hoc commands
ssh-agent bash

create file with private key in /home/ec2-user/.ssh/key.pem

add private key to known keys 
ssh-add ~/.ssh/key.pem

run first ansible command
ansible example -m ping -u ec2-user

run the command with become root in the end
ansible example -a "df -h" -b





